    <span class="course-arrow">&raquo;</span> <div class="course-title"><h4>ELL253 Critical Thinking Skills</h4></div>
    <div class="course-descr">
      The goal of this course is for students to develop their critical thinking skills while examining important social issues
      of the day. Students will develop their skills of deduction, argument and debate.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="clear"></div>
</div>
