  <div class="course">
    <span class="course-arrow">&raquo;</span> <div class="course-title"><h4>SOC252 Sociology</h4></div>
    <div class="course-descr">
      Fundamental concepts and principles of sociology, with emphasis on social organization, social control,
      social change and stratification, social institutions, social processes, and social relationships. Genesis
      of social maladjustments, attitudes, and behaviors in the person, the family, and the community. Social
